Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.94,0:00:17.72,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Something's just not right
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.45,0:00:21.99,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在追尋著什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.42,0:00:26.60,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經習慣了謊言 現在也一樣 fake your eyes
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.46,0:00:32.74,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The start of century
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.10,0:00:36.24,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切毫無定數
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.27,0:00:41.31,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使一個人也不能哭泣軟弱 hate myself
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.61,0:00:51.09,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與真實的痛苦相反的是 埋藏在心中的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.58,0:00:59.90,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在 映射出來 朝著兩個人所決定的未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.19,0:01:03.54,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's only my destiny
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.79,0:01:06.91,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝著沒有盡頭的黑暗前行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.26,0:01:13.25,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裏有未知的明天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.54,0:01:18.25,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,oh yeah.You're going nowhere.It's only destiny
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.51,0:01:21.52,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切實的前行著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.81,0:01:28.86,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感受現在 You're in my heart
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.95,0:01:32.90,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're in my heart
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.30,0:22:33.50,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是等待  刺激的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.50,0:22:40.00,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,眼前所見的  全部是重要的所謂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.00,0:22:52.40,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,失去的東西是恐怖的  但我們之間還什麼也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.40,0:22:53.70,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah　yeah  yeah
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.70,0:22:59.80,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,在這藍藍的地球上  無限重複未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.80,0:23:04.90,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,can make me free　想要感覺這種跳動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.90,0:23:06.30,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah  yeah  yeah
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.30,0:23:12.30,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,這個心情飛舞升起 染滿天空與大海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.30,0:23:22.10,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,緊緊抱住你 想要飛起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.70,0:23:24.90,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah  yeah  yeah
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.90,0:23:31.00,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,這個心情飛舞升起 染滿天空與大海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.00,0:23:41.30,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,緊緊抱住你 想要飛起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.60,0:00:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,命運中亦有推理的線索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.30,0:00:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,錯綜複雜的謎團終有撥雲見日的一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.50,0:00:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天是不可思議的綁架事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.30,0:00:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英語的含義令人費解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.90,0:00:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的是一個外表看似小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.40,0:00:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,智慧卻過於常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.50,0:00:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字是 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.50,0:04:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.50,0:04:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太有意思了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.40,0:04:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,動物們真是可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.30,0:04:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特別是白獅子的特技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.90,0:04:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是絕技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.10,0:04:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為獅子是表演的主角嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.50,0:04:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.70,0:04:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,獅子還被做成了手機鏈呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.40,0:04:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的 這個吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.00,0:04:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可愛吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.70,0:04:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在表演開始之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.20,0:04:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在商店發現的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.30,0:04:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和灰原一起買的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.60,0:04:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳也對這種東西感興趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.50,0:04:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對於那個整天什麼都不管 只知道血腥神秘事件的某人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.70,0:04:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可什麼也沒說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.80,0:04:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要你管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.80,0:04:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是誰 那個被圍住的叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.40,0:05:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是這個馬戲表演的主辦人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.80,0:05:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘭笛·霍克先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.80,0:05:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出生在美國南部奧克拉荷馬市的石油大王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.70,0:05:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說最初收集死去的動物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.90,0:05:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的女兒安妮和斐盧德也在和動物打交道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.80,0:05:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至於現在 是世界各地舉行馬戲表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.70,0:05:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.70,0:05:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看這個冊子的最後一頁不是有他的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.30,0:05:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近的興趣是在表演的同時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.70,0:05:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進行環球旅行並訪問了很多國家的動物園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.00,0:05:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巡迴表演的時候如果不帶保鏢的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.40,0:05:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會被團團包圍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.60,0:05:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只能自己保護自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.40,0:05:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在電視的特別節目上有發過言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.30,0:05:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日語說得相當流利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.10,0:05:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.90,0:05:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,霍克先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.70,0:05:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使是一句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.20,0:05:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弄錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.40,0:06:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是霍克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.70,0:06:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你又在開玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.10,0:06:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你要把表演的一半收入捐給世界各地的動物園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.40,0:06:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.70,0:06:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.50,0:06:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3年沒有來日本了有什麼感想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.90,0:06:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說點什麼吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.20,0:06:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,霍克先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.00,0:06:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,霍克先生 霍克先生 拜託了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.40,0:06:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能一下子回答你們所有人的問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.40,0:06:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來自芝加哥的男人(前篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.20,0:06:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被這麼多人包圍 還真是為難啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.90,0:06:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是瀟灑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.30,0:06:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到這裏連保鏢也不帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.80,0:06:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被這麼多人包圍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.70,0:06:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自作自受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.50,0:06:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼說 我們就幫幫他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.80,0:07:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被這麼多人重重包圍也真夠慘的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.10,0:07:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.50,0:07:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以說 我剛剛就已經說過 我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.30,0:07:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 找到了 找到了 湯姆斯先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.10,0:07:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,湯姆斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.90,0:07:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個人不是霍克先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.70,0:07:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是站在那邊我們叔叔的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.50,0:07:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是做英語教師的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.60,0:07:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.50,0:07:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.00,0:07:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點走啦 湯姆斯叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.80,0:07:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家不是說好了一起去飯店吃午飯的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.50,0:07:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來啦 快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.20,0:07:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.10,0:07:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了孩子們我才能得救
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.10,0:07:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然經常有人說我和霍克先生很像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.50,0:07:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是像這次一樣的誤會還是第一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.40,0:07:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道這樣 不如變裝一下好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.20,0:08:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變裝了更容易讓人懷疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.70,0:08:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你真的那麼喜歡Paul & Annie的動物表演嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.20,0:08:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢 是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.60,0:08:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們的表演最精彩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.70,0:08:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.30,0:08:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼都想要這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.20,0:08:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以就來日本了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.80,0:08:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那個東西我們也買了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.40,0:08:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是這個手機鏈在全世界都很暢銷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.60,0:08:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不需要特地跑到日本來買啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.40,0:08:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看看這個手機鏈的裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.70,0:08:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是寫了"Made In Japan"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.80,0:08:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要買到寫了這個東西的 就一定要到這裏來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.70,0:08:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得 是收藏家收藏的物件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.00,0:08:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.00,0:08:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的意外真是太不幸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.80,0:08:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,表演結束後約好見面的朋友也沒見到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.80,0:08:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,見到一個長頭髮的男子了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.90,0:09:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 因為人太多 所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.20,0:09:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過你倒是很清楚嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.10,0:09:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個人不是霍克先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.30,0:09:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是語言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.90,0:09:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,語... 語言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.70,0:09:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.70,0:09:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛叔叔在說"不能"的意思時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.60,0:09:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把「kant」說成了「ka:nt」 是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.20,0:09:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是昆斯區的英語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.00,0:09:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在被很多人包圍的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.70,0:09:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作為一個地道的南部人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.80,0:09:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說出了英國口音的英語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.30,0:09:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就覺得有點不對勁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.80,0:09:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.70,0:09:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在電視上看見的霍克先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.60,0:09:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是個帶有南部口音相當豪爽的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.40,0:09:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.00,0:09:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仔細比較相冊照片的霍克先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.20,0:09:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,臉是不一樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.30,0:09:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是日本記者弄錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.50,0:09:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不是沒有道理的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.40,0:09:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像外國人很難識別日本人的臉一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.40,0:09:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日本人也只是覺得頭髮 膚色很像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.80,0:09:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以就弄錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.60,0:10:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你太厲害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.80,0:10:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是叫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.30,0:10:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詹姆斯·布蘭克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.60,0:10:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.80,0:10:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,江戶川柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.50,0:10:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.40,0:10:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,江戶川
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.60,0:10:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,江戶川 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.90,0:10:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,江戶川 柯南 偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.40,0:10:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偵探可不是只有柯南一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.70,0:10:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們都是偵探團的一員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.60,0:10:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.90,0:10:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.20,0:10:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢 夏洛克·福爾摩斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.00,0:10:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你們就是貝克街偵探隊咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.00,0:10:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貝克街
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.10,0:10:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個是幫福爾摩斯收集情報的貝克街小孩們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.60,0:10:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貝克街是我出生的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.40,0:10:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 好不容易認識了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.40,0:10:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作為禮物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.40,0:10:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到我非常喜歡的店裏請你們吃一頓大餐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.40,0:11:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是開車來的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.40,0:11:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是這麼多人 就沒有你的位置了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.10,0:11:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK OK 我開我租的廂型車去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.20,0:11:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下 我現在去開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.80,0:11:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我的駕駛技術不太好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.30,0:11:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就由你來駕駛吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.90,0:11:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,右邊方向盤的車太難開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.80,0:11:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔 不習慣右邊方向盤的車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.40,0:11:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就說明你現在不住在英國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.20,0:11:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢 是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.90,0:11:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出生在福爾摩斯的倫敦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.10,0:11:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻是長在芝加哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.40,0:11:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾·卡彭住過的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.10,0:11:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對那個人有沒有什麼感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.20,0:11:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.30,0:11:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.40,0:12:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是那樣就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.60,0:12:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.60,0:12:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們是員警
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.40,0:12:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這車是你的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.10,0:12:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 是我租的車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.20,0:12:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.60,0:12:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實際上這是一輛被盜的車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.10,0:12:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.20,0:12:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一周前做了被盜遺失登記
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.10,0:12:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請說一下你租車的地點以及當時的情況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.20,0:12:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有你的姓名及居住的酒店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.50,0:12:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站著說不太好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.40,0:12:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到小巷對面的警車上談吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.70,0:12:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.00,0:13:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會佔用你太多時間的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.50,0:13:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.90,0:13:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請上車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.40,0:13:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想起來 我的朋友在等我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.70,0:13:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能不能讓我告訴他們我要晚一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.60,0:13:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.60,0:13:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.00,0:13:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老實一點進去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.10,0:13:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.90,0:13:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼東西掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.70,0:13:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是一個手機鏈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.00,0:13:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.50,0:13:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.10,0:14:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手指被弄傷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.10,0:14:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弄傷就弄傷吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.10,0:14:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們不是員警吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.30,0:14:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.30,0:14:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是被包圍的爆發戶嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.90,0:14:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是 我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.40,0:14:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,熱衷於可愛的動物 讓你賺了不少錢吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.50,0:14:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,分給我們一點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.00,0:14:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.80,0:14:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經過了40分鐘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.50,0:14:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真慢啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.20,0:14:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.40,0:14:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肚子都餓扁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.00,0:14:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那博士在這裏等著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.90,0:14:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們大家去看看情況吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.30,0:14:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.70,0:15:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從這裏可以走過去的停車場數量並不多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.30,0:15:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,灰原也一起去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.10,0:15:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這裏吧 停車場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.40,0:15:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詹姆斯先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.90,0:15:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 在這裏嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.80,0:15:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又不是貓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.80,0:15:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詹姆斯先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.20,0:15:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.00,0:15:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了 一定是這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.30,0:15:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詹姆斯先生的廂型車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.90,0:15:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛員的位子前面有一個小獅子玩偶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.70,0:15:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是裏面誰也沒有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.40,0:15:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,門就這麼開著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.10,0:15:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鑰匙也這麼插在這
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.60,0:15:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.60,0:15:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在找誰嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.60,0:15:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是要找乘這輛車的長鬍子外國人的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.90,0:15:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和兩個穿風衣的男人一起去那邊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.70,0:16:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.20,0:16:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.20,0:16:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.10,0:16:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.30,0:16:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.20,0:16:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.60,0:16:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是獅子的手機鏈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.90,0:16:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是詹姆斯先生的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.80,0:16:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是這樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.90,0:16:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是在這裏乘了另一輛車走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.10,0:16:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.90,0:16:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詹姆斯先生說過要和朋友見面的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.40,0:16:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道那個外國人把我們給忘記了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.30,0:16:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和別人去什麼地方吃飯去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.00,0:16:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.30,0:16:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.00,0:16:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能詹姆斯先生被捲入什麼事件裏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.00,0:17:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看 這個手機鏈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.70,0:17:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P和&和A被整齊地塗了血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.90,0:17:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許是想對後來找他的我們傳達什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.50,0:17:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好了 那
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.80,0:17:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不快點向員警
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.50,0:17:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,報案的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.20,0:17:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.20,0:17:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.20,0:17:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.40,0:17:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P&A
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.40,0:17:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是容易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.40,0:17:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下這個爆發戶的子女會付多少錢呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.20,0:17:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少也要5億日元
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.10,0:17:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個傢伙對陌生的動物園也會付那麼多錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.90,0:17:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是錢多得不得了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.50,0:18:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是多虧了這部車跟真警車一模一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.30,0:18:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有我們勇敢的有名望的霍克先生能被團團包圍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.80,0:18:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連保鏢也不帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.90,0:18:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,錯了 我不是霍克先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.60,0:18:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詹姆斯·布蘭克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.80,0:18:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們弄錯人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.20,0:18:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詹姆斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.80,0:18:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被團團包圍後 接下來就是中央情報局了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.50,0:18:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.10,0:18:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是詹姆斯·龐德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.60,0:18:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了 誰都無所謂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.30,0:18:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.90,0:18:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在到我們的老巢之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.50,0:18:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要老實點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.90,0:18:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,007先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.70,0:18:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不如 這樣好好領悟一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.00,0:18:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如何拿你的贖身錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.50,0:19:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們可有絕妙的手段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.40,0:19:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我想看的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.20,0:19:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是你們的本事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.90,0:19:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.40,0:19:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從剛才我們就說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.70,0:19:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有個帶眼鏡的長鬍子的外國人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.50,0:19:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被捲入什麼事件裏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.10,0:19:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有可能是被綁架了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.00,0:19:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你們並沒有親眼看見綁架的畫面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.50,0:19:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且帶眼鏡和有鬍子的外國人很多 沒辦法找啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.30,0:19:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果有照片什麼的就另當別論了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.70,0:19:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有啊 要照片的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.10,0:20:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看啊 就是這張臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.40,0:20:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘭笛·霍克先生啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.10,0:20:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是他的話就沒有問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.00,0:20:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才在收音機節目裏出現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.20,0:20:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.60,0:20:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是和蘭笛·霍克很像的詹姆斯先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.80,0:20:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個收音機的節目是現場直播的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.40,0:20:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在也在播放中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.20,0:20:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 恐怕是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.60,0:20:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.30,0:20:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果犯人把詹姆斯錯當成了霍克而綁架了的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.00,0:20:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就應該會確認霍克先生的播音節目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.80,0:20:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 如果那樣的話 不就馬上被發現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.60,0:20:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果發現綁錯人以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.40,0:20:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先 就會沒命的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.50,0:20:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.40,0:21:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼蘭笛·霍克會出現在收音機節目裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.50,0:21:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 那你是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.60,0:21:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以剛才我說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.20,0:21:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們弄錯人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.70,0:21:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該死 怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.30,0:21:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.40,0:21:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經被這個人看到我們的臉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.70,0:21:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,殺掉他就可以了 殺掉他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.50,0:21:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.70,0:21:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想抱著渾身是血的屍體在市區兜風嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.20,0:21:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要把他打到腦漿迸裂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.60,0:21:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然就得按原計劃
